<TEXT>
<P>
 Scott W. McEwen, Jeffrey R. Davis, Susan D. Moriarty and Michael F. Wilson 
have joined Higgs, Fletcher &amp; Mack as associates. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
