(34) ran for a first down. STEVE DYKES / Los Angeles Times; Photo, USC's Ricky 
Ervins breaks tackle en route to 14-yard touchdown run with 1:10 to play, 
lifting Trojans to 17-10 victory over Michigan. LORI SHEPLER / Los Angeles 
Times 
</P>
